{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/zh/docs/tutorial/manual/grammar","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"F2","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis/f2","docs":[{"slug":"tutorial/manual","title":{"zh":"教程","en":"Tutorial"},"order":1},{"slug":"api/chart","title":{"zh":"图表","en":"Chart"},"order":1},{"slug":"api/graphic","title":{"zh":"绘图","en":"Graphic"},"order":2}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"F2 同 G2 一样，基于《The Grammar of Graphics》(Leland Wilkinson 著)一书所提的图形理论。该理论是一套用来描述所有统计图形深层特性的语法规则，该语法回答了『什么是统计图形』这一问题，以自底向上的方式组织最基本的元素形成更高级的元素。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以对于 F2 来说，"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没有具体的图表类型的概念，所有的图表都是通过组合不同的图形语法元素形成的"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，这些图形语法元素包括："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最基础的部分是你想要可视化的"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/data","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据"}]},{"type":"text","value":"以及一系列将数据中的变量对应到"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/attribute","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"图形属性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的映射；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/geometry","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"几何标记"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，可以理解为你在图表中实际看到的图形元素，如点、线、多边形等，每个几何标记对象含有多个图形属性，F2 图形语法的核心就是建立数据中的一系列变量到图形属性的映射；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/scale","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"度量"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，作为数据空间到图形属性空间的转换桥梁，每一个图形属性都对应着一个或者多个度量；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/coordinate","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坐标系"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，描述了数据是如何映射到图形所在的平面的，一个几何标记在不同坐标系下会有不同的表现。目前 F2 提供了笛卡尔坐标系、极坐标系两种坐标系；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辅助元素是为了增强图表的可读性和可理解性，F2 中的辅助元素包含坐标轴 Axis、图例 Legend、提示信息 Tooltip、静态辅助标记 Guide。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以，在 F2 中，我们通常这么描述一张图表：一张图表就是从数据到几何标记对象的图形属性的一个映射，此外图形中还可能包含数据的统计变换，最后绘制在某个特定的坐标系中。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更多内容请阅读以下篇章："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/understanding-f2-charts","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"图表组成"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.yuque.com/antv/f2/data","target":"_self","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"elem